\textbf{Key Findings:}

\begin{itemize}
	\item \textbf{Bloch Sphere} reveals the geometric rotation: the state vector rotates from the equator toward the target state $|11\rangle$
	\item \textbf{State City} quantifies probability: success probability increases from 0.25 to 1.0 across iterations
	\item \textbf{Circuit Diagram} shows structural elements: Oracle and Diffusion operators are clearly visible
\end{itemize}

